
Short Notice for the bravest

Required packages (Ubuntu 18.04 LTS standard repo)

* to build: binutils-arm-linux-gnueabi (hf on MacOSX)
* to run on a PC: 
  * qemu-system-arm and qemu-user-static, or
  * arm/v7 capable container runtime

Build with "make". 

Test it with "make qrun" with the qemu installed,
or "make drun" to run with arm/v7 capable container runtime,
or copy the binary to a Raspberry PI

